b'' b'' b'a friend of mine is seeing an acupuncturist and' b'wants to know if there is any danger of getting' b'aids from the needles.' b'' b'\task the practitioner whether he uses the pre-sterilized disposable' b'needles, or if he reuses needles, sterilizing them between use. in the' b"former case there's no conceivable way to get aids from the needles. in" b"the latter case it's highly unlikely (though many practitioners use the" b'disposable variety anyway).' b'' b'it is illegal to perform acupuncture with unsterilized needles. no licensed' b'practitioner would dare do this. also there is not a single documented case' b"of transmission of aids via acupuncture needles. i wouldn't worry about it." b'--' b'******************************************************************************' b'robert greenstein what the fool cannot learn he laughs at, thinking' b'of latent idiocy m. corelli' 